31.1.2022 ❤️
Pov : I know I'm quite late for this one , didn't really wanted to post this as I was willing to keep all the moments up till me , but my people around wanted me to put this one . . . this day is closest to my heart !  can't ever thank enough my mom for the things she does for me not only on my speacial days but also on my worst days . I know I always have her back no matter what . I love you tonsss maa 🧿 thank you family for the speacial appearance on my speacial day ! Love you all 💝 and always grateful for all of the sweetest beings I've got in my life , who all are always ready to cheer me up . ✨ Cheers to the year full of new beginnings ahead 🥂
